        <div class="row twowrap">
            <h3>建寺功德</h3>
            <span>CONTRIBUTION TO TAMPLE BUILDING</span>
            <p>佛说：“供养佛殿和文字等同于供养我的真身，功德永远不会耗尽”。</p>
            <p>若人发心起塔、建寺、造像，如是诸人等，如见无数佛，自成无上道，广度无数众。三宝门中福好求，一文种下万文收。一沙一石都承载着佛法的事业，没一份发心都融入佛陀的功德海洋。</p>
            <figure>
                <img src="/assets/images/d.png" alt="">
            </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="row threewrap">
            <h3>
                填写祈愿卡
            </h3>
            <form action="#" class="threewrap-form">
                <div class="threewrap-form-one">
                    <figure class="threewrap-form-one-top">
                        <img src="/assets/images/yuan.png" alt="">
                    </figure>
                    <div class="row threewrap-form-one-middle">
                        <div class="col-xs-10">
                            <textarea class="form-control" rows="3" placeholder="愿所有众生(在此填写愿望)"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-2 threewrap-form-one-middle-right">
                            <figure>
                                <img src="/assets/images/yuan-right.png" alt="">
                            </figure>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <figure class="threewrap-form-one-bottom">
                        <img src="/assets/images/yuan-bottom.png" alt="">
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="row threewrap-form-submit">
                    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-default col-xs-6 col-xs-offset-3" value="确认">
                </div>

            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="row fourwrap">
            <h3>已有<span>169</span>人许愿</h3>
            <p>此许愿卡完全免费，填写完成后，经审核，然后寺庙僧众诵经祈福，把许愿卡挂在五台山贡布神山。愿每个人的愿望也都能实现。</p>

